                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14577.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Silliman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vera Cruz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-12T15:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 12, 1915—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President’s note was delivered to General Carranza this morning. At his request I
                    read it to him in Spanish. There was no comment whatever. After pause I
                    proceeded to discuss other matters with him.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
